column2:
Basic rules
1. The soul-killing battle is divided into four types of factories: Olympus， Ocean， Thebes， and Underworld. Different doll factories are opened every day. You can get 20 levels cleared every day， which can be accumulated if not used.

Formation rules
1. In the soul-crushing combat function，two formations will be opened，and you will use two teams at the same time to challenge.
2. Star Gods cannot be reused between two teams.
3. The development information of the two teams will be directly read from the data on the external lineup，and no additional development is required.
4. The beast gods of the two teams can be set separately.
5. Star Gods must be placed in all empty slots before the battle can begin.

column2:
Rules of the Challenge
1. All players above level 40 can participate in Clash of Kings; Clash of Kings is a season settlement system, and each season lasts for 1 week.
2. During the opening of the season, players can engage in unlimited matching and battles.
3. During the battle, the system will read the player's current lineup for the battle.

Points rules
1. The player’s initial score is 1000 points, and the rank is First Class Sword Fighter I; the rank is divided into 15 ranks in total.
2. Each rank has corresponding points requirements. Among them, there are upper limits for the number of Light Diamond Warriors, God Warriors and Gods of War. They need to rank 200, 50, and 10 in the Battle of Kings zone and reach the corresponding points. Promote to relevant rank
3. Each challenge will be based on the player's current rank and the point difference with the target. Points will be added to the winner and points will be deducted to the loser.
4. When each season starts, the initial points of the current season will be reset based on the final points of the previous season.

Battle report rules
1. Every player-related game (battle report when challenging or being challenged) will be saved in the player's battle report record
2. The battle report can save up to 20 records, which are sorted in chronological order. The new battle report will replace the old battle report.
3. Each battle report is kept for 3 days and will be automatically deleted after 3 days.
4. Players can send the battle report to the guild channel so that other guild members can watch the battle report of the battle.

Bonus rules
1. Players will have 4 task rewards to receive every day: participate in the Clash of Kings 5/10 times, and win the Clash of Kings 2/5 times; complete the rewards to receive them
2. When players upgrade to a new rank in each season, they can receive rewards corresponding to that rank.
3. At the end of each season, season settlement rewards

column2:
Challenge description
1. PVP is a personal arena. You can improve your ranking by challenging other players in this server.
2. You can challenge 10 times for free every day， and then you can use 10 crown stones to purchase times. The free times are reset at 05:00 every day.
3. When you successfully challenge a player with a higher ranking，you will be replaced in that player's ranking: When you are successfully challenged by a player with a lower ranking，you will also be replaced in that player's ranking.

Reward description
1. Each time the challenge is successful, you can receive a treasure box reward and choose 1 treasure box among 3 treasure boxes.
2. When a player's historical highest ranking reaches a certain level, he or she can immediately receive a one-time ranking reward.
3. At 22:00 every day, the system will issue settlement rewards based on the player’s ranking.
4. The new server will immediately start the Arena activity, and you can get additional settlement rewards on the 3rd day after the server is launched.

column2: The battle failed and the automatic challenge has been stopped.

Challenge Rules
1. The Twelve Stars Palace is divided into 12 levels. Each level has 3 randomly selected opponents for challenge.
2. The difficulty of the opponent is divided into easy (1 star)，normal (2 stars)，and difficult (3 stars). You can get different number of stars by challenging different difficulties.
3. In each level， defeat one of the opponents to enter the next level.
4. After each challenge，3 random attribute bonuses will appear. Players can choose 1 of them to obtain. The attribute effects can be superimposed during the current gameplay.
5. Successfully defeating all levels is considered as passing the level.
6. The twelve zodiac signs can be reset once a day

Bonus rules
1. Every time you challenge players，you can get rewards
2. The higher the difficulty of the challenge，the better the rewards will be.
3. Challenge players to get stars. Accumulate stars to get a star treasure chest. After resetting the gameplay，the star treasure chest will be reset.
4. After every three levels of challenge，players will get a mysterious treasure box，which can be opened once for free.
